Package services.persistence.dao.impl

Class FacadeImpl

java.lang.Object
services.persistence.dao.impl.FacadeImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IElementDAO, IFacade, IManagerDAO, ITeamDAO, ITournamentDAO
public class FacadeImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFacade
Singleton class. It groups all DAO's methods, to have only one access point to the persistence level
See Also:
IFacade, ManagerDAOImpl, TeamDAOImpl, TournamentDAOImpl, ElementDAOImpl
